    "Name": "Pegasus Scout Hover Tank",
    "UIName": "Pegasus Scout Hover Tank (3058 Upgrade)",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Pegasus Scout Hover Tank (3058 Upgrade)</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Ferro-Fibrous</color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Inner Sphere</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>9/14 (Hover)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>140 Fusion</color></b>\n\nThe Pegasus is a popular recon hovercraft due to its good speed, decent armor, and respectable firepower. It can be found in almost all militaries, having been introduced during the First Succession War.\n\nAfter the Truce of Tukayyid, the DCMS began an upgrade of the Pegasus hovertank. The newer model replaces the internal combustion engine with a 140-rated fusion engine and the weapons array with twin SRM-6 racks and a Medium Pulse Laser. It also adds a Guardian ECM, a TAG system, and a Beagle Active Probe.",
